Completed PAW competitive positioning battlecard at docs/research/paw-positioning-snapshot-q1-2026.md. Compared 5 alternatives (ChatGPT, Claude.ai, Lindy.ai, Notion AI, Zapier AI) across autonomy depth, human control, reporting quality, and setup friction. Extracted 3 defensible homepage claims. Identified memory system as underplayed differentiator. Key finding: PAW is unique in combining goal decomposition + supervised autonomy + operational cost telemetry.
